# Proof of Sovereignty (PoSov)

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph "Validator Weight Calculation"
        
        Stake[Economic Stake]
        Users[Users Hosted]
        Uptime[Uptime]
        Imports[Imports Facilitated]
        
        Stake --> Weight[Validator Weight w_v]
        Users --> Weight
        Uptime --> Weight
        Imports --> Weight
        
        Weight --> Proposer[Block Proposer Selection]
    end
    
    note over Weight: w_v = stake_v × (1 + ρ_v)<br/>where ρ_v = λ₁(users/|U|) + λ₂(uptime/T) + λ₃(imports/Σ)
    
    style Stake fill:#e94560,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Users fill:#3498db,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Weight fill:#f39c12,stroke:#333,color:#000
```

## Consensus Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant V1 as Validator 1
    participant V2 as Validator 2
    participant V3 as Validator 3
    participant C as Chain
    
    V1->>V1: Propose block
    V1->>C: Broadcast proposal
    V2->>C: Attest (vote)
    V3->>C: Attest (vote)
    
    C->>C: Count weighted votes
    Note over C: Requires 2/3+ weighted votes<br/>for finality
    
    C->>V1: Block finalized
    C->>V2: Block finalized
    C->>V3: Block finalized
```

